nodes.computeCode:
def compute(self):
    '''
        1) get data from inputs
        2) do stuff
        3) put data to outputs
        4) call output execs
    '''
    inDirection = self.inEnum.getData()
    if inDirection == Direction.Right:
        self.outEnum.setData(Direction.Left)
    if inDirection == Direction.Left:
        self.outEnum.setData(Direction.Right)
    if inDirection == Direction.Up:
        self.outEnum.setData(Direction.Down)
    if inDirection == Direction.Down:
        self.outEnum.setData(Direction.Up)
    self.outExec.call()
